snippet.title: Argo - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Play Argo for FREE on Steam! Download now: http://store.steampowered.com/app/530700

Argo is a hardcore tactical first-person shooter, in which players take on the role of a mercenary, and fight across various unrestricted locations on the 62 km² Malden terrain. The game features three competitive 5-vs-5 game modes, plus a cooperative sandbox game mode with randomized objectives. Argo is now available as a FREE game on Steam.

Learn more about Argo's 5-vs-5 competitive game modes:
Clash - https://youtu.be/n8QuAaqGFBs
Link - https://youtu.be/qQcWcHHnhTA
Raid - https://youtu.be/N9cTssyZA5Y
 
Website - http://www.projectargo.net
Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/projectargogame
Twitter - https://twitter.com/projectargogame
